<h3 id="Select-ListBox">ListBox</h3>

<p>        
    In order to render a multi-select input of type listbox list you will need to use the 
    <code>@@Html.BsSelectFor</code> helper extension and 
    decorate your model property with <code>[BsControl(BsControlType.ListBox)]</code>.
</p>

